  "imageAlt": "HeroQuest The Mage of the Mirror Box",
  "description": [
    {
      "paragraph": "The Mage of the Mirror is an expansion for the classic board game HeroQuest. This expansion was first released in 1991 and introduces a new quest and additional miniatures to the original game. The storyline of the expansion revolves around a powerful mage who has been trapped in a magical mirror and seeks to escape."
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "The expansion includes a new quest scenario and additional miniatures. Players take on the roles of the heroes, as they embark on a quest to free the princess."
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "With its engaging storyline, HeroQuest: The Mage of the Mirror is a must-have for fans of the original HeroQuest game. It offers players the opportunity to continue their adventures in the fantasy world of HeroQuest and face new challenges as they battle against the forces of evil."
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "This expansion is designed to be used in conjunction with the original HeroQuest game, and players will need the core box to fully enjoy the new content and features introduced in The Mage of the Mirror."
    }
  ],
